# Ingested GitHub issues live here after analysis, regardless of outcome:
#   `promoted`          → a proposal was created from this issue
#   `promoted-multiple` → several proposals were carved out
#   `dismissed`         → analysis completed but no proposal is warranted
# Every file is named `github#<number>-<slug>.md` and embeds the original
# issue body + comments snapshot so the GitHub thread is recoverable offline.
